  "title": "Senior BCD Technology Development Device Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develops and optimizes BCD process technology and devices for power applications, involving TCAD simulations, device layout, characterization, and bench testing</li>\n  <li>Develop and integrate new BCD device architectures and process modules for company BCD platforms.</li>\n  <li>Conduct TCAD simulations to understand device behavior and calibrate simulation models to match experimental results.</li>\n  <li>Design and lay out device test structures and new BCD device platforms.</li>\n  <li>Analyze device performance and reliability through bench testing and data collection.</li>\n  <li>Work with cross-functional teams, including the modeling team, to satisfy customer needs and develop advanced device models.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Degree in<strong> </strong>Physics or Electrical Engineering.</li>\n  <li>Min 3 year of expereince in<strong> </strong>TCAD (Technology Computer-Aided Design) tools for simulation and calibration.</li>\n  <li>Experience with device layout, design rule checks, and test structure generation.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of BCD process development and device characterization techniques.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br>\n<strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
